GovSecure | 3rd-Party AI Vendor Risk Review
• Approve with conditions - vendor may be used only after defined remediation items, contract
terms, configuration changes, or internal controls are completed.
• Defer - review cannot close because critical evidence is missing or the scope is still changing.
• Reject - vendor risk is too high, controls are insufficient, or the use case is not acceptable.
Practical rule Do not approve a vendor just because a business team already likes the
demo. Demos are theater. Due diligence is rent.
